get attri
| Feature      | Description                                                              |
| ------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| ğŸ“Œ Purpose   | Gets the **value of any HTML attribute** (visible or hidden)             |
| ğŸ” Can fetch | `value`, `href`, `type`, `placeholder`, `class`, `data-*`, etc.          |
| ğŸ§  Works on  | `<input>`, `<a>`, `<div>`, custom elements                               |
| âœ… Best for   | Input values, link targets, button types, hidden data                    |
| ğŸ“˜ Example   | `element.getAttribute("value")`<br>From: `<input value="baby">` â†’ `baby` |


